# NETWORK::NETWORK_GET_LAST_VEL_RECEIVED_OVER_NETWORK

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **VECTOR**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns the last received velocity of a clone entity. Don't use it on local entities

Used by NetBlender
